'From Squeak 2.1 of June 30, 1998 on 13 August 1998 at 2:25:14 pm'!"Change Set:		OwnerFixDoitsDate:			13 August 1998Author:			Dan Ingalls, Scott WallaceGet rid of redundant DropShadows, and nil the owner fields of morphs that are unknown by their apparent owners."!"Postscript:Executable statements after this comment quote..."Smalltalk garbageCollect.(DropShadowMorph allInstances select:	[:m | m hasSubmorphs and: [m firstSubmorph owner ~~ m]]) do: [:m | m delete].Morph repairMorphsUnknownToTheirOwners!